\ndirect evidence that our decoder is robust to one-dimensional, correlated\nerrors that span the lattice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 19:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2020 05:24:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 21:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
